Package com.groq.sdk.models.embeddings

Class EmbeddingRequest

java.lang.Object
com.groq.sdk.models.embeddings.EmbeddingRequest
public class EmbeddingRequest extends Object
Represents a request for generating text embeddings. Contains the input texts and model parameters for embedding generation.

Embeddings are numerical representations of text that capture semantic meaning and can be used for similarity search, clustering, and other NLP tasks.
